<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.4">
<l>ūḻiyil peritāl nāḻikai. yeṉṉu moṇcuṭar tuyiṉṟatā leṉṉu</l>
<l>māḻiyum pulampu maṉṟilu muṟaṅkā teṉṟalun tīyiṉiṟ koṭitām</l>
<l>tōḻiyō veṉṉun tuṇaimulai yarakkuñ collumi ṉeṉceykē ṉeṉṉu</l>
<l>mēḻaiyeṉ poṉṉuk keṉṉiṉain tiruntā yiṭaventai yentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“A few minutes is surely as great as an eon,” she says;</l>
<l rend="indent">“the bright sun sleeps, for sure” she says.</l>
<l>“The sea sobs, the black ibis does not sleep,</l>
<l rend="indent">and the southern breeze will have the cruelty of fire,</l>
<l>[Dear] friend,” she says. She presses both her breasts [in anguish].</l>
<l rend="indent">“Please tell me, what do I do?” she says.</l>
<l>What were you intending for my precious simple [girl],</l>
<l rend="indent">lord father of Iṭaventai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
